###########################
### UPLOAD
###########################

### Upload de arquivo único (requer ADMIN/STAFF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upload/single
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=seu_token_aqui
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="imagem.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./imagem.jpg
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload de múltiplos arquivos (requer ADMIN/STAFF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/upload/multiple
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=seu_token_aqui
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="imagem1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./imagem1.jpg
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="imagem2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./imagem2.jpg
------FormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###########################
### LISTAGEM PÚBLICA
###########################

### Listar eventos públicos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos

### Listar cursos públicos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cursos
